    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into thin fries</p><p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with a small drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong>, give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until crispy</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-chicken-breast-burger-w-sweet-potato-fries-and-garlic-mayo/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>chicken breast[s]</strong> into strips</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken breast strips</strong>, your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> to a bowl, give everything a good mix up then set aside</p><p>Add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a plate with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> and mix everything together \u2013 this is your <strong>breadcrumb mixture</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-chicken-breast-burger-w-sweet-potato-fries-and-garlic-mayo/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Press the <strong>chicken breast strips</strong> into the <strong>breadcrumb mixture</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over \u2013 these are your <strong>breaded chicken strips</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-chicken-breast-burger-w-sweet-potato-fries-and-garlic-mayo/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>breaded chicken breast strips </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>15-18 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until cooked through (no pink meat!) and crispy \u2013 this is your <strong>crispy breaded chicken</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-chicken-breast-burger-w-sweet-potato-fries-and-garlic-mayo/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce </strong>and pat dry with kitchen paper, then shred it finely</p><p>Dice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>finely</p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining tomato[es] </strong>finely into rounds</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-chicken-breast-burger-w-sweet-potato-fries-and-garlic-mayo/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and your <strong>mayo </strong>in a small bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a separate bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-chicken-breast-burger-w-sweet-potato-fries-and-garlic-mayo/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is nearly cooked, slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat and add the <strong>brioche halves</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and charred</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/crispy-fried-chicken-breast-burger-w-sweet-potato-fries-and-garlic-mayo/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Spread the <strong>warmed brioche bun</strong> with the<strong> garlic mayo</strong>, then add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>, <strong>sliced tomato </strong>and<strong> crispy breaded chicken breast strips</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> fries</strong>,<strong> diced tomato </strong>and <strong>remaining shredded lettuce </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>dressing </strong>over the<strong> </strong>salad</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
